[ADDITION] Migrated settings to version 2

[REMOVAL] Entity attributes (homeassistant.legacy_entity_attributes setting) has been removed. This means that entities discovered by Zigbee2MQTT will no longer have entity attributes (Home Assistant entity attributes are accessed via e.g. states.binary_sensor.my_sensor.attributes).

[REMOVAL] The permit_join setting has been removed, use the frontend or MQTT to permit joining.

For more details, see https://github.com/Koenkk/zigbee2mqtt/discussions/24198